dct_title_s: South America--Chile, Golfo de Arauco (Raster Image)
dct_description_sm: Prepared and published by the Defense Mapping Agency Hydrographic Center. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Soundings in meters." Includes source diagram. Georeferenced nautical chart. Map no. 22312. Inset maps of: Bahia De Lota, Bahia De Coronel, Caleta Chivilingo, Caleta Colcura, Bahia Llico, Caleta Laraquete. "From a Chilean government chart of 1922."
This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
